WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.210
Good morning, family. I'm excited to

00:00:02.220 --> 00:00:04.130
be with you again today; I think this is

00:00:04.140 --> 00:00:06.950
the third video in a row.

00:00:06.960 --> 00:00:09.650
This video is pretty serious.

00:00:09.660 --> 00:00:12.290
The Lord has put on my heart—I'm

00:00:12.290 --> 00:00:12.300
going to

00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:13.730
tell you the things I've been

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:15.110
praying about.

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:19.310
I've been praying over Italy and

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:21.650
all the little tremors and the

00:00:21.660 --> 00:00:24.290
volcano.

00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:26.330
I'm going to tell you what I saw. I

00:00:26.340 --> 00:00:28.189
was caught up in the Spirit. I was just

00:00:28.199 --> 00:00:29.870
praying in the

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:31.790
Spirit, I was worshiping, and all of a

00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:35.090
sudden I was shot up. I was

00:00:35.100 --> 00:00:39.350
looking over Italy, and

00:00:39.360 --> 00:00:42.069
Italy was so small.

00:00:42.069 --> 00:00:42.079
I

00:00:42.079 --> 00:00:45.170
was so

00:00:45.170 --> 00:00:45.180
high—I

00:00:45.180 --> 00:00:47.090
guess that's the way I want

00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:49.369
to say it—I was really, really high and I

00:00:49.379 --> 00:00:52.369
was looking down. All of a sudden, I

00:00:52.379 --> 00:00:56.270
could see

00:00:56.280 --> 00:01:00.229
a black blanket over the water over Italy. It looked like

00:01:00.239 --> 00:01:03.349
a thick cloud,

00:01:03.359 --> 00:01:06.890
but it was

00:01:06.890 --> 00:01:06.900
as

00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:11.090
black as

00:01:11.090 --> 00:01:11.100
molasses—very,

00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:15.649
very dark. It was all over

00:01:15.649 --> 00:01:15.659
the water and there

00:01:15.659 --> 00:01:18.410
were

00:01:20.580 --> 00:01:24.890
black

00:01:24.900 --> 00:01:27.590
clouds going through all the houses.

00:01:27.600 --> 00:01:30.350
It looked like

00:01:30.360 --> 00:01:33.890
a smog all

00:01:33.900 --> 00:01:36.469
around the houses.

00:01:36.479 --> 00:01:39.830
I could see the rooftops of the homes

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:41.870
because I was up, and I could see

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:43.969
the lights on in the houses.

00:01:43.969 --> 00:01:43.979
Angels were

00:01:43.979 --> 00:01:45.950
descending into

00:01:45.950 --> 00:01:45.960
Italy.

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:48.789
Above, the Lord pointed my attention

00:01:48.799 --> 00:01:54.469
to a massive circle, a

00:01:54.479 --> 00:01:57.590
humongous portal that was over the

00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:00.469
country of Italy.

00:02:00.469 --> 00:02:00.479
It

00:02:00.479 --> 00:02:03.410
was

00:02:03.410 --> 00:02:03.420
over

00:02:03.420 --> 00:02:05.749
where the earthquake

00:02:05.759 --> 00:02:07.670
happened last night, where I told you the volcano

00:02:07.670 --> 00:02:07.680
is

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:11.330
at by Pompeii. There was this massive portal

00:02:11.330 --> 00:02:11.340
and there were angels in it.

00:02:11.340 --> 00:02:15.410
The angels were coming out

00:02:15.410 --> 00:02:15.420
of

00:02:15.420 --> 00:02:17.150
this massive portal, and the portal was like it was breathing—it was alive. It was swirling, and there

00:02:17.160 --> 00:02:19.850
were

00:02:27.540 --> 00:02:29.990
clouds all in it.

00:02:29.990 --> 00:02:30.000
It

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:31.970
looked

00:02:31.980 --> 00:02:34.550
like it was opening up, and all of a

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:36.830
sudden these angels started coming out

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:39.729
of this massive

00:02:39.729 --> 00:02:39.739
portal—thousands

00:02:39.739 --> 00:02:43.430
of them. They were all

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:47.030
coming down like a staircase. It was

00:02:47.040 --> 00:02:47.869
like

00:02:47.879 --> 00:02:50.630
they were all descending, but

00:02:50.640 --> 00:02:53.150
they were lined up

00:02:55.620 --> 00:02:59.030
like

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:01.309
soldiers coming out of this massive

00:03:01.319 --> 00:03:03.650
portal over Italy. It looked like

00:03:03.660 --> 00:03:05.809
they were coming downstairs, but I could

00:03:05.819 --> 00:03:08.750
not see stairs. Through the portal,

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:11.570
there were clouds coming out as the

00:03:11.580 --> 00:03:14.210
portal was breathing and

00:03:14.220 --> 00:03:16.009
turning. It was swirling; it was alive.

00:03:16.019 --> 00:03:19.250
The clouds coming out of

00:03:19.260 --> 00:03:20.410
the portal

00:03:20.410 --> 00:03:20.420
were

00:03:20.420 --> 00:03:24.470
humongous and

00:03:24.470 --> 00:03:24.480
beautiful—pink,

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:27.050
blue,

00:03:27.060 --> 00:03:30.050
and

00:03:32.809 --> 00:03:32.819
purple.

00:03:35.159 --> 00:03:37.910
I believe it was Heaven.

00:03:37.920 --> 00:03:40.430
These angels were all

00:03:40.440 --> 00:03:42.470
coming down and

00:03:42.470 --> 00:03:42.480
descending

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:44.990
onto the Earth.

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:47.690
When they got to a certain

00:03:47.700 --> 00:03:52.190
place in the atmosphere between the

00:03:52.200 --> 00:03:54.649
portal and the Earth, they started to

00:03:54.659 --> 00:03:57.589
spread out like ants all over

00:03:57.599 --> 00:03:59.449
the place. They started scattering

00:03:59.459 --> 00:04:02.210
and they were coming even faster down

00:04:02.220 --> 00:04:05.630
onto those homes.

00:04:05.640 --> 00:04:08.809
All of a sudden, each angel was going to

00:04:08.819 --> 00:04:09.949
a

00:04:09.959 --> 00:04:11.750
place; they were on a mission,

00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:13.190
moving at the

00:04:13.200 --> 00:04:14.750
speed of light.

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:16.670
They were moving down, and they all

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:20.030
had beautiful robes and gowns

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:22.069
on. It was the

00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:23.450
most amazing thing. The whole time,

00:04:23.460 --> 00:04:26.749
I'm sitting here in this chair

00:04:26.759 --> 00:04:28.850
praying in the Spirit and

00:04:28.860 --> 00:04:30.830
seeing all this,

00:04:32.100 --> 00:04:34.430
soaking it all in.

00:04:34.440 --> 00:04:36.950
I'm trying so

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:39.650
hard to explain everything the Lord

00:04:39.660 --> 00:04:42.590
showed me in detail:

00:04:46.249 --> 00:04:46.259
the

00:04:49.979 --> 00:04:52.189
black smog. I was asking the Lord what all that

00:04:52.189 --> 00:04:52.199
black smog was.

00:04:52.199 --> 00:04:54.350
He showed me that

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:57.350
from coast to

00:04:57.360 --> 00:04:59.510
coast,

00:04:59.520 --> 00:05:01.430
there's a lot

00:05:01.440 --> 00:05:03.830
of sex trafficking in Italy.

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:05.510
I don't know if people don't know

00:05:05.520 --> 00:05:07.610
about it, but he

00:05:07.620 --> 00:05:09.110
was showing that there was a lot of

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:12.409
corruption and trafficking in Italy.

00:05:12.419 --> 00:05:14.510
There was

00:05:14.520 --> 00:05:15.770
sand and things he

00:05:15.770 --> 00:05:15.780
was

00:05:15.780 --> 00:05:19.670
showing me about this.

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:24.350
Those angels were coming down, going to

00:05:24.350 --> 00:05:24.360
these homes,

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:27.350
and they were making

00:05:27.350 --> 00:05:27.360
a

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:29.450
motion

00:05:29.460 --> 00:05:32.090
with their hand, like

00:05:32.100 --> 00:05:34.430
'Come on,'telling the people to leave. It was a warning. Every angel was waving the people to come on.

00:05:49.080 --> 00:05:53.390
They

00:05:53.400 --> 00:05:55.850
did this

00:05:55.860 --> 00:05:57.350
for several minutes.

00:05:57.360 --> 00:05:58.670
In the Spirit, you couldn't really

00:05:58.680 --> 00:06:00.890
tell a time frame, but you could sense

00:06:00.900 --> 00:06:04.070
an urgency on their faces.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:06.650
It felt like such an

00:06:06.660 --> 00:06:09.230
urgency of a warning, telling the people

00:06:09.240 --> 00:06:11.930
to leave.

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:15.529
They didn't say anything; I could just

00:06:15.539 --> 00:06:17.930
see by their body language that they were in

00:06:17.940 --> 00:06:21.490
a hurry. All of a sudden,

00:06:21.500 --> 00:06:24.790
all of the angels

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:28.610
stopped their arms,

00:06:28.610 --> 00:06:28.620
and

00:06:28.620 --> 00:06:30.770
I knew people were praying. I could

00:06:30.780 --> 00:06:33.950
feel the intercessory prayers from the

00:06:33.960 --> 00:06:36.050
saints, from the Christians, from

00:06:36.060 --> 00:06:38.809
people interceding for Italy in the

00:06:38.819 --> 00:06:40.730
Spirit, praying in tongues.

00:06:40.740 --> 00:06:42.770
You could

00:06:42.770 --> 00:06:42.780
feel

00:06:42.780 --> 00:06:44.870
the blanket of prayer coming

00:06:44.880 --> 00:06:47.510
out of that portal.

00:06:56.039 --> 00:06:57.890
You could feel the

00:06:57.900 --> 00:07:01.730
intercessory prayer going on.

00:07:01.740 --> 00:07:06.050
All of a sudden, all the angels froze

00:07:06.050 --> 00:07:06.060
and

00:07:06.060 --> 00:07:09.350
turned

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:12.110
their bodies to look back up

00:07:12.120 --> 00:07:16.070
to the massive swirling light,

00:07:16.080 --> 00:07:19.189
the portal.

00:07:26.460 --> 00:07:28.370
All of a sudden, they

00:07:31.440 --> 00:07:32.510
started shooting back up

00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:34.909
into that portal, and then it

00:07:34.909 --> 00:07:34.919
was over.

00:07:34.919 --> 00:07:37.430
Then the Lord took me

00:07:37.430 --> 00:07:37.440
to

00:07:37.440 --> 00:07:41.390
another part of the

00:07:41.400 --> 00:07:44.809
vision. He said, 'I want you to

00:07:44.819 --> 00:07:47.809
focus on the canary.

00:07:47.819 --> 00:07:51.050
A canary Braden, what is the meaning of

00:07:51.060 --> 00:07:53.570
a canary in a coal mine?

00:07:53.580 --> 00:07:55.129
Study this

00:07:55.129 --> 00:07:55.139
out.'I

00:07:55.139 --> 00:07:58.909
saw a yellow canary in a cave,

00:07:58.919 --> 00:08:02.510
and there were gases. I could see a

00:08:37.919 --> 00:08:41.750
gas

00:08:41.760 --> 00:08:44.810
coming up out of the ground like

00:08:44.810 --> 00:08:44.820
a smog.

00:08:44.820 --> 00:08:47.090
The canary was swinging in a cage. I saw this birdcage in the spirit realm. I saw the canary on the little swing, swinging back and forth and chirping. All of a

00:08:47.100 --> 00:08:49.370
sudden, I looked down because I could see this mist-like gas coming up out of the ground. I took my eyes off the canary,

00:08:49.370 --> 00:08:49.380
and

00:08:49.380 --> 00:08:50.810
when

00:08:50.820 --> 00:08:52.970
I looked back, the

00:08:52.980 --> 00:08:55.850
canary was dead in the bottom of

00:08:55.850 --> 00:08:55.860
the

00:08:55.860 --> 00:08:58.070
cage—lifeless

00:08:58.070 --> 00:08:58.080
and

00:08:58.080 --> 00:09:01.009
completely gone.

00:09:01.019 --> 00:09:02.990
It happened so

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:06.290
quickly; the gases came up and

00:09:06.300 --> 00:09:10.670
took the canary out. This is

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:12.470
part of the vision the Lord showed me

00:09:12.480 --> 00:09:15.110
about the angels

00:09:15.110 --> 00:09:15.120
and

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:17.210
this gas coming up out of the ground

00:09:17.220 --> 00:09:19.730
in Italy. I don't know what that

00:09:19.730 --> 00:09:19.740
was—if

00:09:19.740 --> 00:09:21.410
it was from

00:09:22.620 --> 00:09:24.650
the volcano

00:09:24.660 --> 00:09:26.930
or whatever.

00:09:26.940 --> 00:09:29.290
But I told you all I saw

00:09:29.300 --> 00:09:31.610
hundreds of thousands of people go home.

00:09:31.620 --> 00:09:34.550
I saw a massive wave coming. The

00:09:34.560 --> 00:09:37.370
Lord said, 'Pay attention to the

00:09:37.370 --> 00:09:37.380
water.'I

00:09:37.380 --> 00:09:39.949
saw the earthquakes in the water, and the

00:09:39.959 --> 00:09:41.449
people weren't paying attention.

00:09:41.459 --> 00:09:43.850
The water was what the Lord kept

00:09:43.860 --> 00:09:45.769
putting my attention to in the past

00:09:45.769 --> 00:09:45.779
visions—look

00:09:45.779 --> 00:09:48.290
at the water

00:09:48.300 --> 00:09:50.570
in the coves.

00:09:50.580 --> 00:09:52.550
He kept pointing me to

00:09:52.560 --> 00:09:53.870
that in the spirit realm. I could see with my spirit

00:09:53.880 --> 00:09:55.730
eyes

00:09:55.730 --> 00:09:55.740
what

00:09:55.740 --> 00:09:56.990
the Lord was

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:59.870
showing me: the water

00:09:59.880 --> 00:10:01.970
in the gulf area right

00:10:01.980 --> 00:10:05.449
there by Pompeii.

00:10:05.459 --> 00:10:07.009
This is just what the

00:10:07.009 --> 00:10:07.019
Lord is

00:10:07.019 --> 00:10:09.530
showing me. I know, like I said,

00:10:09.540 --> 00:10:12.710
a major 4.4, I believe, happened last

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:15.170
night. I saw all the rocks and the

00:10:15.180 --> 00:10:16.790
devastation, the people, and the sirens

00:10:16.800 --> 00:10:19.610
going off. There was a video my wife

00:10:19.620 --> 00:10:20.750
gave me

00:10:20.760 --> 00:10:23.690
from

00:10:23.690 --> 00:10:23.700
someone

00:10:23.700 --> 00:10:26.810
on Facebook; they

00:10:26.820 --> 00:10:29.090
were putting it on their feed there, and

00:10:29.100 --> 00:10:30.530
she was showing me, saying, 'Listen to

00:10:30.530 --> 00:10:30.540
this.'So

00:10:30.540 --> 00:10:31.910
I looked at it and I was like, 'Oh

00:10:31.920 --> 00:10:33.530
my goodness.'I guess this just

00:10:33.540 --> 00:10:35.990
happened yesterday, last

00:10:35.990 --> 00:10:36.000
night—it

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:39.050
was our

00:10:39.050 --> 00:10:39.060
night—so

00:10:39.060 --> 00:10:42.350
not even 12 to 24 hours ago. The

00:10:42.350 --> 00:10:42.360
electric

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:44.750
grid situation

00:10:44.750 --> 00:10:44.760
is

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:46.850
escalating, and

00:10:46.860 --> 00:10:48.650
things are really getting

00:10:48.660 --> 00:10:51.710
intense. Okay, number two: for

00:10:51.720 --> 00:10:55.670
the past week, even from last

00:10:55.670 --> 00:10:55.680
Monday—not

00:10:55.680 --> 00:10:58.550
yesterday Monday, but the week

00:10:58.550 --> 00:10:58.560
prior—three

00:10:58.560 --> 00:11:01.910
times now the Lord has spoken

00:11:01.920 --> 00:11:04.970
to me about the electric grid in

00:11:04.980 --> 00:11:08.509
America, telling me, 'Pray over the

00:11:08.519 --> 00:11:11.569
electric grid. This is very serious.'I saw

00:11:11.579 --> 00:11:14.329
a cyberattack or it was a false

00:11:14.339 --> 00:11:16.910
flag attack. Like I

00:11:16.920 --> 00:11:19.250
said, I'm not going to just flat out

00:11:19.260 --> 00:11:21.250
say it was Russia or whoever;

00:11:21.260 --> 00:11:24.650
I'm telling you I saw something go on

00:11:24.660 --> 00:11:27.470
with our electric grid, and all of a

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:31.190
sudden power went out in New York and

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:33.769
major cities. It was completely dark

00:11:33.779 --> 00:11:36.350
everywhere because of what happened on

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:40.250
this electric grid issue. And so He said,

00:11:40.260 --> 00:11:42.050
'You're not taking this serious

00:11:42.050 --> 00:11:42.060
enough.'He

00:11:42.060 --> 00:11:43.730
warned me, saying, 'You need to pray about

00:11:43.740 --> 00:11:46.610
this more intently

00:11:46.620 --> 00:11:49.250
because of what is being planned and

00:11:51.769 --> 00:11:51.779
plotted.'I

00:11:52.860 --> 00:11:57.050
saw when the electric grid went down,

00:11:57.060 --> 00:11:59.389
for some people, it had the opportunity

00:11:59.399 --> 00:12:02.269
to be down for over three weeks. I saw

00:12:02.279 --> 00:12:04.430
the number three—for over three

00:12:04.440 --> 00:12:06.410
weeks. I saw

00:12:06.410 --> 00:12:06.420
a

00:12:06.420 --> 00:12:08.150
calendar, and I could see the

00:12:08.160 --> 00:12:10.370
days go by with people being without

00:12:10.380 --> 00:12:13.190
power. The Lord was warning me

00:12:13.200 --> 00:12:15.650
about these major cities and about this

00:12:15.660 --> 00:12:18.410
plot against America and about the

00:12:18.420 --> 00:12:21.290
power grid. Now, I don't know a timeframe

00:12:21.290 --> 00:12:21.300
or

00:12:21.300 --> 00:12:23.389
anything else about

00:12:23.399 --> 00:12:25.730
that. All I know is I'm interceding for

00:12:25.740 --> 00:12:28.430
this. This is on top of the

00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:31.130
Italy thing that He brought to my

00:12:31.140 --> 00:12:33.650
attention, warning me about it.

00:12:33.660 --> 00:12:36.050
Like I tried to tell you all about

00:12:36.060 --> 00:12:37.630
what He showed me a year ago about

00:12:37.640 --> 00:12:40.130
investing into a generator that had

00:12:40.140 --> 00:12:43.310
three fuel types—propane, gas, and

00:12:43.320 --> 00:12:46.670
natural gas—and having

00:12:46.680 --> 00:12:48.889
electricity for what was coming in the

00:12:48.899 --> 00:12:52.670
future, powering

00:12:52.670 --> 00:12:52.680
your home,

00:12:52.680 --> 00:12:55.550
finding ways to power your home through

00:12:55.560 --> 00:12:57.530
solar.

00:12:57.540 --> 00:12:59.269
They sell lights on Amazon, there's

00:12:59.279 --> 00:13:01.490
candles, there's all kinds of stuff for

00:13:01.500 --> 00:13:03.050
people to

00:13:03.060 --> 00:13:06.170
have light.

00:13:06.180 --> 00:13:08.870
I don't want to ever preach fear; I don't

00:13:08.880 --> 00:13:10.850
want to be a Debbie

00:13:10.860 --> 00:13:11.990
Downer and come on here and go

00:13:11.990 --> 00:13:12.000
wacko

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:15.290
all the time, but I get these

00:13:15.300 --> 00:13:17.269
things from the Spirit of God, these

00:13:17.279 --> 00:13:20.030
warnings, and they're very intense. He

00:13:20.040 --> 00:13:22.490
warns me about things.

00:13:22.500 --> 00:13:24.650
For instance,

00:13:24.660 --> 00:13:28.069
I was praying over

00:13:28.079 --> 00:13:31.730
